<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>You're Invited!</title>
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: auto; background-color: white; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
      <h2 style="color: #333;">Hi {{name}},</h2>

      <p>
        {{inviter_name}} from <strong>{{company_name}}</strong> has invited you to join our platform!
      </p>

      <p>
        By joining, you’ll be able to collaborate with your team, access company resources, and take advantage of all the tools designed to help you succeed.
      </p>

      {{#if invite_link}}
      <p style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
        <a href="{{invite_link}}" target="_blank" style="background-color: #1a73e8; color: white; padding: 12px 20px; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">
          Accept Invitation
        </a>
      </p>
      {{/if}}

      <p>
        If the button above doesn’t work, you can copy and paste this link into your browser: <br />
        <a href="{{invite_link}}" target="_blank">{{invite_link}}</a>
      </p>

      <p>
        We’re excited to have you on board and can’t wait for you to explore what we’ve built together!
      </p>

      <p>Best regards,<br />
      <strong>The {{company_name}} Team</strong></p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
